---
import { Heart, Brain, Zap } from 'lucide-react';
import FeatureCard from './FeatureCard';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 relative">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        About AutiMind
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Founded in 2023, AutiMind began with a mission to develop AI solutions for autism support. As we evolved, we expanded our expertise across diverse industries, ultimately building AstroLMS - the learning management system we had envisioned from the start. Today, we're an AI software development company specializing in custom AI solutions and intelligent automation, with proven expertise through successful products like AstroLMS and ZServed.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <FeatureCard 
        icon={Heart}
        title="Custom AI Solutions"
        description="We develop tailored AI applications that solve specific business challenges, from automation to intelligent data processing."
        client:load
      />
      
      <FeatureCard 
        icon={Brain}
        title="Proven Expertise"
        description="Our successful products like AstroLMS and ZServed demonstrate our ability to build AI-powered solutions that transform industries."
        client:load
      />
      
      <FeatureCard 
        icon={Zap}
        title="Industry Agnostic"
        description="From education to legal services, we apply AI and emerging technologies to solve complex challenges across diverse business sectors."
        client:load
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>